					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "To create a jQuerh instance do the following:\n\n\thtml jQuery   <-- this gives an instance of aJQueryClass\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<-- send the following messages (and others) to hre instanc\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t#new\t<- currently active dom ielement -- returns an instance of JQueryInstance.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t#this\t  <- currently active dom ielement -- returns an instance of JQueryInstance.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t#id:\t\t<- the ID of the DOM node that this applies to\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thtml jQuery experession: '#foo'    <-- this is CSS selector for element ids\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thtml jQuery Id: 'foo'   <---- this uses the ID of 'foo'\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thtml jQuery: '#foo'   <-- same as 1()\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t#class    <- the css class name"
			}
		]
